    {
      "chinese": "[---]\r\n普悠瑪部落有許多法規，如偷牛會被棍棒打，搶他人妻被罰一頭或兩頭牛，犯姦淫就脫光兩人的衣服並坐在雙方家族人前，接受指責、羞辱。有爭執、打架，耆老們就召集參與者到集會所互相討論，若耆老們判定哪一方有錯，就按耆老們的規定解決問題，雙方不會反對。",
      "ab": "na Puyuma i, ulraya a sadru a marekamenimeni tu kinuretan kana tremakaw dra gung. tu lumekaw dar. na emaraw dratu kataguwin dra trau i, tu pasabungaw dra saya, adri i, dra druwaya dra gung. na matratrakaw matratraep i, tu paluwaluwaw nadru na miyadruwa i nguwayan kantu nirumaenan aw tu punangay, tu lrimusaw. \r\n[===]\r\nna masaseredr, na madrikudrikul i, tu daulraw nadru na ulraya tu inuleutran aw tu padradrayaraw i palakuwan. an kemuret dratu kuwadakudayan kana mipamelriyan dra i manay i, uniyan dra semubeli kanadru kana maaidrangan na parisarisan.",
